3.0.1 to 3.1.0:

* Implemented some animation functionality

3.0.0 to 3.0.1:

* Added support for setting the tooltip to strings up to 127 instead of 63 characters (via `SuperNotifyIcon.Text` instead of `SuperNotifyIcon.NotifyIcon.Text`)

2.0.3 to 3.0.0:

* Implemented the drop functionality from FluffyApp
* Class renamed from NotifyIconLoc to SuperNotifyIcon
* Now uses native Windows APIs on Windows 7 for location detection
* Optimised the pre-Win7 location detection
* Fixed numerous amounts of crashes that can occur with pre-Win7 location detection

2.0.2 to 2.0.3:

* Added some exceptions that are thrown when getting an invalid notification area size, to see if this is an issue or not

2.0.1 to 2.0.2:

* Made the NotifyArea class public
* Reduced the maximum attempts for each call to GetLocation()

2.0.0 to 2.0.1:

* Fixed values going outside the 0-255 RGB range

1.4.0 to 2.0.0:

* Significantly more accurate detection algorithm

1.3.0 to 1.4.0:

* More accurate detection algorithm
* The default accuracy has been changed from 1 to 0, resulting in ~30ms matches

1.2.0 to 1.3.0:

* The screenshot area has been changed from the entire taskbar to only the notification area

1.1.0 to 1.2.0:

* Fixed issues of RGB calculations going over 255 or under 0

1.0.0 to 1.1.0:

* Always return -1, -1 if a fullscreen app is detected